      <p><strong>Find a loan request to support.</strong></p>
      <%= link_to(image_tag("arrowbutton.png", :alt => "Make A Loan"), loan_requests_path) %>
  </div>

  <div class="showcase">
      <h2>Get Repaid</h2>
      <p>Get updates as the borrowers you support succeed and repay their loans.</p>
      <h2>Repeat</h2>
      <p>When borrowers repay, you can use that money to support a new loan and empower another person! You can also choose to donate or withdraw your funds. </p>
  </div>
